reviewText:
It is unfortunate that large profitable disc manufacturers
are minimizing their expenditures for big profits by using poor
discs quality instead something like the "Kodak 100 years DVD"
which will give customers the chance to have their generations to
enjoy the world renowned Agatha Christie's Miss Marple & Poirot
Series.  Until then just get your blu-ray copy of "Agatha Christie's
Miss Marple Adaptaions - Season 4 from Amazon-com.
